Maximizing the impact of research through openness. Because science works best when research is open.

Journal Profile

International Journal of Early Childhood Special Educationpublishes original research articles and review articles covering a wide range of subjects within the biomedical sciences. The journal will accept both basic and translational research.

About the Journal

Editor Spotlight

International Journal of Early Childhood Special Education maintains an Editorial Board of practicing researchers from around the world, to ensure manuscripts are handled by editors who are experts in the field of study.

Meet the Editorial Board

Special Issues

We currently have a number of Special Issues open for submission. Special Issues highlight emerging areas of research within a field, or provide a venue for a deeper investigation into an existing research area.

About Special Issue
